item.title: Go baby Go israel - First year summery
item.dc:creator: gavin.wood
item.description:
What an impressive effort for your first year! You seem to have modified a very wide variety of cars! Have you tried reaching out to any FIRST Robotics teams in Israel? There are several very good teams that bring a lot of technical expertise to the table and are always looking for new opportunities for outreach. Just wondering if that was something your group might be interested in?
